      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 308340.0,
      "end_time": 310940.0,
      "text": "Rob: Mmm, right, before logging off let’s"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 310940.0,
      "end_time": 312420.0,
      "text": "review today’s vocabulary."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 312420.0,
      "end_time": 315870.0,
      "text": "Catherine: OK, we had FOMO, an acronym"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 315870.0,
      "end_time": 317260.0,
      "text": "that means Fear Of Missing Out."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 319990.0,
      "text": "Something that I get quite a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 319100.0,
      "end_time": 321400.0,
      "text": "Rob: And that makes you also a phubber -"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 321400.0,
      "end_time": 322980.0,
      "text": "people who ignore the real people around"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 322980.0,
      "end_time": 324740.0,
      "text": "them because they are concentrating on"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 324747.0,
      "end_time": 325810.0,
      "text": "their phones."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 325810.0,
      "end_time": 327783.0,
      "text": "Catherine: Yes, I do think I’m probably"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 327783.0,
      "end_time": 329655.0,
      "text": "addicted to my phone. I have a"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 329655.0,
      "end_time": 332123.0,
      "text": "psychological and physical need to have"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 332124.0,
      "end_time": 334440.0,
      "text": "it. My smartphone is my drug."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 334440.0,
      "end_time": 335900.0,
      "text": "Rob: Wow, and you look at it"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 335900.0,
      "end_time": 337580.0,
      "text": "compulsively. You can’t stop looking at it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 337580.0,
      "end_time": 339700.0,
      "text": "you do it again and again, don't you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 339700.0,
      "end_time": 341820.0,
      "text": "Catherine: It's sadly true, Rob. To keep in"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 341820.0,
      "end_time": 343940.0,
      "text": "touch with someone is to contact them"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 343940.0,
      "end_time": 345469.0,
      "text": "and share your news regularly."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 345470.0,
      "end_time": 347742.0,
      "text": "Rob: And if you do that yourself by"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 347742.0,
      "end_time": 349720.0,
      "text": "actually meeting them, then you are doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 349720.0,
      "end_time": 352000.0,
      "text": "it in person. And that brings us to the end"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 352500.0,
      "end_time": 353580.0,
      "text": "of today’s programme."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 353580.0,
      "end_time": 356600.0,
      "text": "Don’t forget you can find us on the usual"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 356600.0,
      "end_time": 357900.0,
      "text": "social media platforms – Facebook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 357900.0,
      "end_time": 360120.0,
      "text": "Twitter, Instagram and YouTube - and on"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 360120.0,
      "end_time": 363320.0,
      "text": "our website at bbclearningenglish.com."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 363420.0,
      "end_time": 364220.0,
      "text": "Bye for now."
    },
    {
